### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@mail.com",
    "password": "admin"
}

### Read all USERS and AUTHORS(only emails)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/users

### Block or Activate USER or AUTHOR

### Change Password
PUT http://localhost:4000/auth/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword" : "user_1",
    "newPassword" : "user1"
}